events.name: Sunday Morning Makers: Sharing on the Plastic Injection Machine!
events.description:
In this session, we will share our journey and learning points from the plastic injection machine project, from forming up the team of volunteers, following the blueprints from preciousplastic.com, learning the skills required such as welding and electronics, the many ups and downs, to finally completing the project! We hope that this sharing will spark your interest in making too!

We will also be teaching you how to make the rope maker!

Come to this sharing session! Bring your friends!
events.location: Sustainable Living Lab (SL2), 111 Middle Rd, Unit 01-02, Singapore 188969
